    "1020102": {
        "Desc": "Chase down the Abyss Mage with Klee (If the Abyss Mage gets more than 50m away, the quest will be failed)",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "1020103": {
        "Desc": "Pursuit I",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "A gateway to a domain! The Abyss Mage must have snuck inside."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Then he has no way out."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Let's keep up the chase."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "*panting* ..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Klee, do you need a rest?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Why don't you wait here while we get your treasure back for you?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "...No, I'm coming with you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "It's my treasure that Mr. Fluffball stole, and it's up to me to get it back!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I admire your courage."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "But these domains can be dangerous."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "Hee-hee, don't worry. Klee is a big girl!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "#Come on, {F#Miss}{M#Mr.} Honorary Knight! Let's goooo!"
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
    "1020114": {
        "Desc": "",
        "Talk": []
    },
    "1020104": {
        "Desc": "Combat I",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "Abyss Mage",
                    "T": "Hmph. You followed me. I must say, I'm impressed."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Abyss Mage",
                    "T": "But this is as far as you will get."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Oh yeah? What are you gonna do?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Abyss Mage",
                    "T": "Mwuhahaha! Ahahahaha!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Abyss Mage",
                    "T": "Oh, the human proclivity to gossip has provided us with everything we need..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Abyss Mage",
                    "T": "We learned that your little red friend had in her possession the most powerful treasure in all of Mondstadt."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Abyss Mage",
                    "T": "That treasure is now in my hands. There is nothing you can do!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Abyss Mage",
                    "T": "Now your precious treasure shall be your undoing!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "No, no, wait! D—Don't touch it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Abyss Mage",
                    "T": "Hah! Oh, how you fret now your predicament is finally clear to you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Abyss Mage",
                    "T": "Now, what have we here — a flame symbol? Mwuhahaha..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Abyss Mage",
                    "T": "*bang*"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "NO!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "I broke the survival rules... \"Explosions can hurt people... Jean can be dreadful...\""
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "This is it... This time I'm done for... *sobs*"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Wait, so Klee's treasure is a bomb!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "That was epic..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "It made short work of that Abyss Mage!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "No wonder Klee was rumored to be the strongest fighter in Mondstadt."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon for one is never picking a fight with her. Ever."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hold on... Why has she gone and run off?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Something to do with the survival rules..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Something to do with Jean..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Seems like it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Well then, let's head to the <color=#00E1FFFF>Knights' headquarters</color> and report to Jean."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
