    "1020201": {
        "Desc": "Go back to the Knights' headquarters and report to Jean",
        "Talk": [
            [
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Klee? You're here too?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "I... *sobbing* I turned myself in."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "...Huh?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "*sobbing* I... M—My bomb... I—I hurt someone..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "*sobbing* I broke the rules... I'll never see the light of day again..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Klee, I need you to answer me. You said someone was injured. Where are they?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Wait! There's been a misunderstanding."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Why is that?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "The person that Klee blew up was an Abyss Mage."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "But... But Mr. Fluffball was only a thief... He didn't deserve to blow up..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Hey, come on now... Paimon already told you that the Abyss Mages are the bad guys..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "And actually, they're the worst kind of bad guys you can imagine. They don't just hate the good guys, they hate all people... Their enemy is... humanity itself."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "Mr. Fluffball... was a bad guy on purpose? ...Mr. Fluffball is the enemy of humanity!?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "Wha... what!? I don't get it!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "This was an oversight on my part."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "I did not tell you these things before because you are still young."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "In fact, the Abyss Order is a hostile force in Mondstadt which has been unusually active lately."
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "Because of Mondstadt's most powerful treasure?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Aha, that's it! Paimon understands now!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "They were tracking down poor Klee because they'd heard rumors about her treasure!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Just like the way Paimon's first reaction was to try and get her hands on... ahh, no— to try and get the facts on the treasure."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "So... does that mean..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "In light of your contribution on this matter, I will allow you to take part in the next Ludi Harpastum."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "Ludi Harpastum! Whoa!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "You got very lucky!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "I'm so happy for you!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "#{M#Mr.}{F#Miss} Honorary Knight, you've gotta come too!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Woop-de-doo, it's a happy ending!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Except..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Klee, where did you hide the treasure to begin with?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "I... Um..."
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Were you trying to blow up the fish in Starfell Lake again?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "I wasn't! I swear I wasn't!"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "(She's giving us that look that means, play along...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_0",
                    "T": "(Uh-oh, Jean noticed it too...)"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Jean",
                    "T": "Klee?"
                },
                {
                    "N": "Klee",
                    "T": "I'll see myself to <color=#00E1FFFF>solitary confinement</color>... *sobbing*"
                },
                {
                    "N": "_1005",
                    "T": "Paimon bets Klee must get bored in there all by herself..."
                }
            ]
        ]
    },
